I'll dissent
I wouldn't quite say that S4 is terrible, but I think it's mostly pretty, pretty bad. The sketches all go on interminably, lots of them are weird rehashes or mashups of earlier material, no Kenny and there's just a sort of general lack of the fun anarchy that was capable of elevating some of the worst material in seasons past.

There are a few great sketches here and there (Everest, Food Ads), but I dislike the 4th seasons enough that watching my S4 DVDs always kind of leaves me in a bad mood.
